Africa T20 Cup bụ asọmpi cricket Twenty20 nke Cricket South Africa haziri
Ọ gosipụtara njikọta nke ndị otu mpaghara South Africa na ndị otu na-anọchite anya mba ndị ọzọ dị n'Africa, gụnyere Kenya, Namibia, na Zimbabwe
Ọ gbara afọ anọ tupu CSA Provincial T20 Cup dochie ya.
E mere mbipụta mbụ nke asọmpi ahụ na Septemba na Ọktoba 2015, dị ka onye bu ụzọ na oge ezumike South Africa nke 2015-16
Ọ bụ Northerns meriri ya, nke meriri KwaZulu-Natal Inland na ngwụcha site na wickets asaa. Emere mbipụta nke abụọ nke asọmpi ahụ na Septemba na Ọktoba 2016
Ọ bụ Eastern Province meriri ya, bụ ndị meriri Northern Cape na ngwụcha site na ọsọ 31.

A kọwaala iko Afrịka T20 dị ka "ihe ngosi na mmepe cricket". Ndị otu South Africa nwere ihe mgbochi dị iche iche na ihe mejupụtara ndị otu ha - ha agaghị enwe ihe karịrị ndị egwuregwu anọ sitere na franchises ọkachamara, ọ dịkarịa ala ndị egwuregwu abụọ na-erubeghị afọ 21, na ọ dịkarị ndị egwuregwu isii na-acha odo odo (gụnyere ọ dịkarịrị ndị Black Africa atọ). Africa T20 Cup mejupụtara oghere fọdụrụ na kalenda South Africa site na ịkagbu Champions League Twenty20
Netwọk telivishọn SuperSport, onye isi na-akwado Cricket South Africa, bụ onye mgbasa ozi nke asọmpi ahụ.

N'afọ 2016, a tụrụ aro na a ga-agbasawanye iko Afrịka T20 n'ọdịnihu iji tinye mba Afrịka ndị ọzọ, dị ka Uganda. Maka mbipụta 2018, ọnụ ọgụgụ ndị otu mụbara site na 16 ruo 20, na mgbakwunye nke ndị otu South Africa nke Limpopo na Mpumalanga, yana nnọchiteanya mba si Ghana na Nigeria. Otú ọ dị, Ghana jụrụ oku Cricket South Africa kpọrọ ka ha sọọ mpi na asọmpi ahụ, Uganda wee dochie ha.
